   "source": [
    "What is a List Comprehension?\n",
    "\n",
    "A list comprehension is a compact way to create a list by applying an expression to each item in an iterable, with an optional condition."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "a2bc44b5",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
